carbon.widget

Interface InsetView

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppBarLayout, AutoCompleteLayout, BottomBar, BottomSheet, Chip, CollapsingToolbarLayout, ConstraintLayout, CoordinatorLayout, DrawerLayout, ExpansionPanel, FastLayout, FlowLayout, FrameLayout, GridLayout, InputLayout, LinearLayout, RadioGroup, RelativeLayout, Snackbar, TableLayout, Toolbar

    public interface InsetView
    Interface of a view with insets. Used by layouts to handle standard system insets added by status bar and navigation bar.
